title: Allyn Robinson discusses Jaco Pastorius with Robert Sturcken
description: Also, check out Allyn paying tribute to Jaco on his New CD released October 1, 2013 www.allynrobinson.com. The first US "studio" recording of Jaco's composition, Amelia, originally recorded live with Allyn in 1972 with Wayne Cochran and The CC Riders.  See www.allynrobinson.com for the whole story and to listen for free. [Interview Summary] Allyn was Robert Sturcken's radio guest on "Nightlife and Music with the Maestro" on The Lake 94.7 FM on January 31, 2012.  Allyn discusses his time playing with Jaco Pastorius in Wayne Cochran and The C.C. Riders and shares several classic anecdotes.
